    public class SketchViewModel
extends androidx.lifecycle.AndroidViewModel
implements androidx.lifecycle.LifecycleObserver
    Viewmodel for the Featured fragment, this view model is lifecycle aware, populates the data needed for the view in the Featured fragment.
